<model>
  <name>uav26_quad</name>
  <version>1.0</version>
  <sdf version="1.10">model.sdf</sdf>
  <description>
    UAV26 X-frame quadrotor for line_tracer closed-loop validation.
    Mounts a downward color + depth camera (D435 사양 모사) and a fake FC
    (gz-sim-multicopter-velocity-control-system) listening on cmd_vel.
  </description>
